 NEPC office  The Deputy Director, Incentives NEPC, Lawal Dalhat, said the portal was created in line with government policy to improve the ease of doing business within the nation.“The platform provides opportunity for all stakeholders, processing government agencies, auditors, exporters and relevant bodies to submit, review and access information regarding processing of claims,” he stressed.“We believe that the automated program will further boost non-oil exports as more exporters will be encouraged to participate in subsequent export transactions.” he said.  To enable commenting and other interactive features, please switch to the more advanced .